item.title: CVE-2023-32984|2024-08-02T15:32:46.596Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20testng%20results%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins TestNG Results Plugin 730.v4c5283037693 and earlier does not escape several values that are parsed from TestNG report files and displayed on the plugin's test information pages, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability exploitable by attackers able to provide a crafted TestNG report file.
